## Description {#details}

Helper class to iterate through stack ids in both metadata (memprof MIB and callsite) and the corresponding ThinLTO summary data structures (<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/callsiteinfo">CallsiteInfo</a> and <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/mibinfo">MIBInfo</a>).

This simplifies implementation of client code which doesn&#39;t need to worry about whether we are operating with IR (Regular LTO), or summary (ThinLTO).
